r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HKN-BLUES-WRITETHRU-T     05-13 0582
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HKN-BLUES-WRITETHRU-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BLUES' POWER PLAYS SHORT OF HIGH VOLTAGE 
EDITORS: FIXES SLUGLINE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JENNIFER FLOYD 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   ST. LOUIS _ The power is still on in the St. Louis Blues' power
play, but the light is definitely flickering.
