<P>
   &UR; By THE EDITORIAL BOARD OF THE INDEPENDENT &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   By sacking Yevgeny Primakov, Russia's modern czar has done both
his country and the international community a grave disservice...
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (375 words) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
