   COXNET TRAVEL 0515 SOUTH CAROLINA STRAND _ The rivers are dark,
the marshes mysterious and the gnarled live oaks with their
filigree of silvery moss hold ancient secrets. The upper coast of
South Carolina, with its natural charms, beckons to the adventure
seeker. (Crouch Thrasher, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
