celebrates the North Georgia city's three rivers with a concert by
Johnny Rivers at Ridge Ferry Park, an arts showcase, a bass
tournament, laser show, boat excursions, performing arts and more.
We take a look at what's up in Rome and focus on the festival.
(Davis, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). MOVED.
