<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-13 13:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5510 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CHILDCARE-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      05-13 1642
