</P>
<P>
   Lamar Alexander _ Well-crafted Web site touches all key bases,
including online volunteer forms. (http://www.lamaralexander.com/).
When Internet search engines initially directed surfers to a
nautical supplies store in Ohio, (http://www.lamaralexander.org/),
the campaign was obliged to buy up that name too.
</P>
