and an insistent chorus, it is the vehicle that former Menudo
member Martin _ he of the pretty face and the boffo appearance on
this year's Grammy awards _ is riding to be the first truly huge
male Latino crossover star. You will listen. You will sing along.
You will, now and in the coming weeks, have no choice. Not that you
want one. By DAVE FERMAN. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment
