refugees as the region's share of an estimated 20,000 promised
shelter in the United States. The agencies will have their work cut
out for them because of education, language and cultural
differences. Agencies not sure when refugees will start arriving,
but Spokane agency says within the next six weeks.
</P>
<P>
   By Gordy Holt. (Story will move in the ``a'' category.)
</P>
