``Tea with Mussolini'' that blurs the events of Mussolini's fascist
regime yet lends to the making of an affecting dramatic period
piece.
</P>
<P>
   By Paula Nechak. (Story will move in the ``e'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   FILM-DREAM (Undated) _ Lust is certainly hinted at in director
