<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-13 20:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6241 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ROSENTHAL-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      05-13 0739
