 &HT;    ``No one could ever say anything against Dr. Lokvam in front of
me.''
 &HT;    After a national day to honor secretaries was initiated in 1952,
Dad (``when he wasn't in surgery'') would take her to lunch.
 &HT;    ``We might just go and get a hamburger, but it was
entertainment,'' she said.
